<span>Gualtherus: αφΡΟΔΙΤαιΔ</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\" https://orcid.org/0000-0003-1030-5679\">Giorgia Capra</a></p>  <p>Shipowners. Olympis son of Hyperbolos; Theugnis son of Eubios; Phryneidas son of Teisandros; Diokles son of...; Aristodamos son of Eubios; Ogeaokos(?) son of Eupheide (?); ...son of Peitharchos; Peisandros son of Agathon; ... son of Teisandros; Apollodoros son of Archidamos; Zopuros son of Naukrates; ...son of Uperbolos; Aischron son of Aristoxenos. To Aphrodite.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>  </p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 36.0851 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a></li><li> Gualtherus 1624 [1625] 2 no.3 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001931\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001931</a></li><li> Franz 1853 5615 add <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001250\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001250</a></li><li> Kaibel 1890 <a href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">401</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072</a></li><li> Hoffmann 1904 5217 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000817\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000817</a></li><li> De Salvo 1992 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002045\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002045</a></li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence.  </div>",
